* Iron Raptor almost found it funny that Firearm didn't exactly know who 
they were, but she guessed that since the change...it was alittle hard for 
anyone to know just who they were.
She sighed.
If Firearm reacted like this, what would the rest of the Maximals think nack 
at base?
Ah well...cross that bridge when she came to it.
But she heard Firearms answer all the same, wonderinf slightly if he knew 
anything at all about the meeting besides the fact that Kluster had called 
it.
But she had a hunch about what it was for.

Iron Raptor watched as Prowl walked up to her, looking at Iris a bit before 
looking back to Prowl.
Fly?
She wondered if this body handled hights better then the last one...but if 
she had wings then it must.
Iron Raptor nodded.*

< Yes...but you realize that once I learn to fly on my own, these carrying 
trips will end...if I ever learn how to use those feathered chicken wings in 
my back...."
